{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_04_01",
  "title": "白石沙季 1話 確かな成長と違和感",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――千紗と沙季が出場した、ユニットバトル決勝前日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day before the unit battle finals with Chisa and Saki participating.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "沙季、お疲れ様。最後の練習は終わったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki‚ good job. Are you done with the final practice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、ついさっき終わったところです\n千紗は……サニピの皆さんと話してますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job to you too. We just finished a moment ago.\nChisa-chan is… talking with everyone from Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても……沙季も千紗も\nここ数日で一気に成長したな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so… both Saki and Chisa\nhave grown so much these past few days.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "顔つきから違うし、ユニットとしての完成度も抜群だ\n一体何をしたらここまで変われるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a difference in your demeanor‚ and it''s complete as a unit.\nWhat did you guys do to change this much?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "つい数日前までは、どうやったらこのユニットが\n良くなるのかずっと悩んでいたんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Until just a few days ago‚ I was constantly\nworried about how to improve our unit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗に言われたんです\n「お姉ちゃんは本当は前に出たいんじゃないの？」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But then Chisa-chan said to me‚\n\"Don't you honestly want to stand out?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "その上、「このままお姉ちゃんが譲るなら、私の方が\n前に出て目立っちゃうんだから」とまで言われまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moreover‚ she even said‚ \"If you keep stepping back‚\nI'll be the one who stands out.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "驚いたな……千紗がそんな大胆なことを言ったのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm surprised… Chisa said something so bold?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "私も驚きましたし、千紗が独り立ちして遠くへ行って\nしまうような気がして寂しくもなりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was surprised too‚ and felt a bit lonely thinking\nChisa was becoming independent and going far away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "ですが……それ以上に千紗がこんなにはっきりと自分の\n気持ちを話してくれたことが嬉しくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… more than that‚ I was happy that\nChisa expressed her feelings so clearly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "何より、私自身の……前に出たいという欲求に\n気付かせてくれて、感謝しているんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Most of all‚ I'm grateful she made me realize\nmy own desire… to step forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……姉妹揃って一皮むけた訳だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… both sisters have really come into their own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、そうですね。……あ、千紗\nそれでは、そろそろ帰りますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ yes‚ that's right. …Ah‚ there's Chisa-chan.\nWell then‚ I'll be heading home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "明日の決勝、楽しみにしていて下さい\n必ず優勝しますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looking forward to tomorrow's final.\nWe will definitely win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7166.666666699995,
          "startTime": 107.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "驚いたな、あそこまで言い切るなんて\nそれだけ自信があるということか……明日が楽しみだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm amazed‚ to declare it so confidently.\nI'm looking forward to tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12266.666666600002,
          "startTime": 118.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "皆さん、今日は私と千紗のパフォーマンスを\n見ていただき、本当にありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ thank you so much for\nwatching my and Chisa's performance today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、今まで皆さんが見たことのない\n私と千紗の姿を見せられたのではと思っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I believe you must have seen a side of us\nthat you've never seen before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "……あら？　千紗ったら照れてるの？\n曲が終わったとたんにいつも通りね……ふふ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? Chisa‚ are you blushing?\nJust like usual as soon as the live ends… haha.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9966.666666599991,
          "startTime": 141.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、改めて……皆さん、本当に\nありがとうございました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ once again…\nThank you so much‚ everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "二人で歌えて本当に良かった\nこれからも……ずっと一緒に頑張ろうね、千紗",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was really great that we could sing together.\nChisa‚ from now on‚ let's keep doing our best together‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "凄い歓声だ……それだけ、二人のステージが\n素晴らしかったということだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What an amazing applause…\nIt just shows how fantastic their performance was.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（この後、二人は見事優勝を果たした）\n（しっかりと労ってお祝いしないとな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（After this‚ they successfully won the competition.）\n（I should congratulate and celebrate with them properly.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4466.666666599991,
          "startTime": 170.1333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4800.000000000011,
          "startTime": 170.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 166.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "沙季、お疲れ様。何してるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki‚ good job. What are you up to?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\nユニットバトルの感想を調べていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ thank you.\nI was checking feedback on the unit battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのライブでも私のことを書いてくれる方は\nいましたけど……今回はその数が凄く多いんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Some people wrote about me during Moon Tempest's live performance…\nBut this time‚ the number is incredibly high!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "今までももちろん楽しかったんですが、千紗との\nユニットで前に出る楽しさや快感を知ってしまいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've always enjoyed it‚ but I've come to know the excitement\nand pleasure of being in the forefront with Chisa in our unit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "それだけ手応えが掴めたのはいいことだな\n月ストの活動にもぜひ生かしてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's good that you've gained so much from it.\nMake sure to apply what you've learned to Moon Tempest too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　……はぁぁ～。決勝の舞台から見た\n観客の皆さんの熱狂する顔が忘れられません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! …Haaah. I can't forget the enthusiastic faces\nof the audience from the finals' stage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "横を見れば、今までにないくらい自信に溢れた\n千紗と目が合って……嬉しくて胸が高鳴って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I looked to the side‚ I met Chisa's eyes‚ filled with\nmore confidence than ever…I felt so happy that my heart was racing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ええっと……沙季？　おーい……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ Saki? Hey…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！\n私、今までやったことがない仕事がしてみたいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nI wanna try something that I never done before!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "決勝の後の打ち上げで千紗とも話してたんです\n「この勢いでいろんなチャレンジがしたいね」って！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I talked to Chisa about it at the post-finals party‚ and we were like‚\n\"Let's take on various challenges with this momentum!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか。分かった、分かったから\n一旦落ち着いてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Alright‚ alright‚\ncalm down for a moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！\nす、すみません、熱くなり過ぎました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hah!\nS-Sorry‚ I got too carried away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski023.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、チャレンジがしたいのは本当ですから\nよろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I really want to take on new challenges‚\nso please‚ I'm counting on you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
