        "en": "It's alright! I don't know\nwhere my charm lies yet!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 301.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski028.m4a",
      "text": "今の私なら、多少過激な衣装であっても\n着こなすことが出来ると思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I can pull off\neven slightly daring outfits now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "待て待て。……次のページに、ここ最近の表紙を\nまとめたから、それを見てから決めてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on. On the next page‚ I've compiled\nrecent cover shots. Take a look before deciding.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 314.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3300.0000000000114,
