      },
      "startTime": 323.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "確認して良かっただろ？　これはお断りしておくよ\nそれで、次なんだが……こういうのはどうだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was it good to check? I'll decline this one for you.\nNow‚ for the next one… How about this type of job?",
