      "text": "あ、この番組……私も知ってます\n確か、バラエティの色が相当強いですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ this program… I'm familiar with it.\nIt's a variety show with pretty strong comedic element‚ right?",
        "id": ""
