      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski031.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。出演出来るアイドルは、可愛いだけじゃなく\n笑いが取れることが条件……ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. The condition for idol appearances is not\njust being cute but also being able to make people laugh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 350.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
