      "text": "鈴村さんやこころのように\n笑いを取れる自信はあるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you have the confidence to make people laugh\nlike Suzumura and Kokoro?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 369.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski034.m4a",
      "text": "……ゆ、優ちゃんとこころちゃんのように……ですか？\nそれは、ちょっと……厳しいものが……",
